# Curated channels that are NOT present in the upstream source playlist.
# merge_extra.py injects every entry below into dhanytv.m3u on each update so
# the weekly auto-update (which REPLACES dhanytv.m3u with the fresh source) can
# never silently drop them. Keep this file as the single home for hand-added
# channels (World Cup, events, etc.). Lines starting with "# <...>" are section
# dividers and are preserved by cleanup_playlist.py.

# <============================================== WorldCup 2026 ===========================================================>

#EXTVLCOPT:http-referrer=https://tvri.go.id/
#KODIPROP:inputstreamaddon=inputstream.adaptive
